description: Returns detailed information about the privacy budgets in a specified membership.

parameters.name: membershipIdentifier
parameters.description: A unique identifier for one of your memberships for a collaboration. The privacy budget is retrieved from the collaboration that this membership belongs to. Accepts a membership ID.

nested_items.name: privacyBudgetSummaries
nested_items.description: An array that summarizes the privacy budgets. The summary includes collaboration information, membership information, privacy budget template information, and privacy budget details.

nested_items.name: id
nested_items.description: The unique identifier of the privacy budget.

nested_items.name: privacyBudgetTemplateId
nested_items.description: The unique identifier of the privacy budget template.

nested_items.name: privacyBudgetTemplateArn
nested_items.description: The ARN of the privacy budget template.

nested_items.name: membershipId
nested_items.description: The identifier for a membership resource.

nested_items.name: membershipArn
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the member who created the privacy budget summary.

nested_items.name: collaborationId
nested_items.description: The unique identifier of the collaboration that contains this privacy budget.

nested_items.name: collaborationArn
nested_items.description: The ARN of the collaboration that contains this privacy budget.

nested_items.name: type
nested_items.description: Specifies the type of the privacy budget.

nested_items.name: createTime
nested_items.description: The time at which the privacy budget was created.

nested_items.name: updateTime
nested_items.description: The most recent time at which the privacy budget was updated.

nested_items.name: differentialPrivacy
nested_items.description: An object that specifies the epsilon parameter and the utility in terms of total aggregations, as well as the remaining aggregations available.

nested_items.name: aggregations
nested_items.description: This information includes the configured epsilon value and the utility in terms of total aggregations, as well as the remaining aggregations.

nested_items.name: type
nested_items.description: The different types of aggregation functions that you can perform.

nested_items.name: maxCount
nested_items.description: The maximum number of aggregation functions that you can perform with the given privacy budget.

nested_items.name: remainingCount
nested_items.description: The remaining number of aggregation functions that can be run with the available privacy budget.

nested_items.name: epsilon
nested_items.description: The epsilon value that you configured.

nested_items.name: nextToken
nested_items.description: The pagination token that's used to fetch the next set of results.
